<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>English IV Exam</title>
<style>
body {
  font-family: Arial;
  background: #f4f6f7;
  padding: 20px;
}
.container {
  background: white;
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  max-width: 600px;
  margin: auto;
}
h1 {
  text-align: center;
}
button {
  padding: 10px;
  background: #2ecc71;
  color: white;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 5px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="container">

<h1>📝 English IV Exam</h1>

<form id="quiz">

<p>1. If I ____ more time, I would study psychology.</p>
<input type="radio" name="q1" value="b"> had<br>
<input type="radio" name="q1" value="a"> have<br>

<p>2. She ____ therapy sessions every week.</p>
<input type="radio" name="q2" value="b"> attends<br>
<input type="radio" name="q2" value="a"> attend<br>

<p>3. If he ____ stressed, he will talk to a psychologist.</p>
<input type="radio" name="q3" value="a"> feels<br>
<input type="radio" name="q3" value="b"> felt<br>

<p>4. They ____ studying memory when the teacher arrived.</p>
<input type="radio" name="q4" value="b"> were<br>
<input type="radio" name="q4" value="a"> are<br>

<p>5. A psychologist ____ people understand emotions.</p>
<input type="radio" name="q5" value="b"> helps<br>
<input type="radio" name="q5" value="a"> help<br>

<p>6. What is psychology?</p>
<input type="radio" name="q6" value="b"> Study of mind and behavior<br>
<input type="radio" name="q6" value="a"> Study of animals<br>

<br><br>
<button type="button" onclick="checkAnswers()">Submit</button>

</form>

<h2 id="result"></h2>

</div>

<script>
function checkAnswers() {
let score = 0;

if(document.querySelector('input[name="q1"]:checked')?.value == "b") score++;
if(document.querySelector('input[name="q2"]:checked')?.value == "b") score++;
if(document.querySelector('input[name="q3"]:checked')?.value == "a") score++;
if(document.querySelector('input[name="q4"]:checked')?.value == "b") score++;
if(document.querySelector('input[name="q5"]:checked')?.value == "b") score++;
if(document.querySelector('input[name="q6"]:checked')?.value == "b") score++;

document.getElementById("result").innerHTML =
"✅ Your score: " + score + "/6";
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
